OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThere will be a mixture of some
OL,6,Fbright or sunny spells along with
OL,7,Foccasional showers, these sometimes
OL,8,Fwintry over higher ground. The strong
OL,9,Fnorthwest winds, early gales over
OL,10,FBuchan, soon moderating.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FStill a few showers this
OL,13,Fevening, wintry on high ground,
OL,14,Fbecoming more isolated then dying out
OL,15,Fovernight as skies become clear. Winds
OL,16,Ffalling light with a frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
