OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA dry and bright day with
OL,6,Fplenty of sunshine, the best in the
OL,7,Fmorning with some high cloud arriving
OL,8,Fin the afternoon. Lighter winds, a
OL,9,Fgentle southerly later.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FSunny,
OL,12,Fbreezy and warm on Tuesday, though
OL,13,Fcooler along North Sea coasts.
OL,14,FCloudier later. Chance of patchy or
OL,15,Frain or showers on Wednesday. Sunshine
OL,16,Fand showers on Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
